1.5.1.name: wordpress/ajax-page-loader-15
1.5.1.description:
Original: AJAX Page Loader will load posts, pages, etc. without reloading entire page. This was my first plugin and is still a little quirky. There is problems working on some themes. I am working a little at a time on this but if anyone wants to contribute, feel free.

Description for 1.5: This is the same plugin as http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/ajax-page-loader/ . But with more of the bugs worked out.

Version 1.5.2 Adds IE6 compatibility.

Many thanks to Luke Howell, author of the original plugin.
